<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/15(Thu.)20 Steps Towards More Self-Directed Learning/Top 10 Ways Coronavirus Will Change Your Life Forever(William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=436&amp;p=454#p454"><![CDATA[
10/15(Thu.)20 Steps Towards More Self-Directed Learning/Top 10 Ways Coronavirus Will Change Your Life Forever(Host:William)<br /><br />Article1:20 Steps Towards More Self-Directed Learning<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.opencolleges.edu.au/informed/features/29-steps-toward-more-self-directed-learning/">https://www.opencolleges.edu.au/informe ... -learning/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Have you ever tried self learning ? If the answer is yes. How did you overcome the obstacles ?<br />2. Have you ever helped your friend learning something or fulfill your friend's goals? You might play music instruments or sports together.<br />3. Do you prefer face to face communicating or online learning ? <br />4. Learning through self-teaching do you have suggestions ?<br />5. People around the world being quarantined now in order to prevent the spread of the virus. How can they practice self study ?<br /><br />Article2:Top 10 Ways Coronavirus Will Change Your Life Forever<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://listverse.com/2020/03/24/top-10-ways-coronoavirus-will-change-your-life-forever/">https://listverse.com/2020/03/24/top-10 ... e-forever/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Among top 10 ways of the articles which one will change your life most ? <br />Will the pandemic change your life ?<br />2. There are 33 millions confirmed cases and 1 million people died from the pandemic. When the pandemic will end ?<br />Is there a way to going back to normal life in the near future ? What is our future ? <br />3. The pandemic affect our live, work, interact, live and even grief for losses. How do you cope with it ? <br />4. Poor people, homeless and people with disability are vulnerable from the pandemic.<br />How the society and government help them ?<br />5. Do you see any unexpected benefits and opportunities from the pandemic ?<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Agenda<br />7:00 pm-7:30 pm Free talk<br />7:30 pm-8:10 pm Session 1 discussion<br />8:10 pm-8:40 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 pm-8:45 pm Break time &amp; Group picture<br />8:45 pm-9:15 pm Session 2 discussion<br />9:15 pm-9:30 pm Presentation<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交500元，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Sun Oct 11, 2020 12:02 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
